- Create, read, update, and delete trucks
  - Track truck details including unit number, year, and notes
  - Modern interface with intuitive year selection

- **Substitute Unit Management**
  - Assign substitute trucks to main units
  - Track substitution periods with start and end dates
  - Prevent double assignments and validate date ranges

- **Activity Logging**
  - Comprehensive logging of all system changes
  - Track who made changes and when
  - View detailed change history with before/after values
  - Filter logs by date range

## Requirements

- PHP >= 8.0
- Laravel 10.x
- MySQL/MariaDB
- Composer
- Node.js & NPM (for asset compilation)
